To create a text-based config

enable
configure terminal
configuration text generate active running save my-filename

To apply a text-based config

enable
configure terminal
configuration text file my-filename apply

To upload config to server

enable
configure terminal
configuration text file my-filename upload scp://root@my-server/path

To fetch config from server

enable
configure terminal
configuration text fetch scp://root@my-server/root/tmp/my-filename
